      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRAVELLING DEAN (2) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (19.30) behind Juan Bandito at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Can go on with it. STAR FERNANDO (8) is a newcomer for the Josh Gatehouse kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles strongly for this and can make an immediate impact. TOP SHELF TED (5) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (16.99) at this track behind Oh Lenny in a Maiden. Expecting another good run. REMEMBER PAL (1) can run a bold race on best form.",
